note: I am a Latinx and a community development practitioner I am also an artist and traveler at heart with a passion for photography as part of my storytelling. I am a storyteller who writes with a sense of passion and detail about the good and bad of our humanity, having worked as community development consultant for 40 years. My passion is to continue to travel and record my experiences through storytelling and photography for my audience, providing advice, reviews, and hopefully inspiration.
